name: Bradshaw
description: i never judge a book by it cover, the same with people, i never judge some one from the out side. take the time to get to know them, you just might see that they aren’t as bad as you thought and become good friends, we are all too quick to judge others because of what they look like or what we think of them on the outside and not from the inside, life is too short to let good people go.
